s://goearthward.com/?page_id=60\" data-key=\"45ecf79d86\" data-product-id=\"23468\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wd-action-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wd-check-icon\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"wd-action-text\">Add to wishlist</span>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"product-element-bottom\">\n\t\n\t\n\t<h3 class=\"wd-entities-title\"><a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product/clear-quartz-crystal-point-earrings/\">Clear Quartz Crystal Point Earrings</a></h3>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wd-product-cats\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product-category/clear-quartz-crystals/\" rel=\"tag\">Clear Quartz Crystals</a><span class=\"wd-meta-sep\">,</span> <a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product-category/crystal-earrings/\" rel=\"tag\">Crystal Earrings</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t<span class=\"price\"><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>89.00</bdi></span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">&ndash;</span> <span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>118.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;89.00 through &#36;118.00</span></span>\n\n\t<div class=\"wd-add-btn wd-add-btn-replace\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product/clear-quartz-crystal-point-earrings/\" aria-describedby=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23468\" data-quantity=\"1\" class=\"button product_type_variable add_to_cart_button add-to-cart-loop\" data-product_id=\"23468\" data-product_sku=\"\" aria-label=\"Select options for &ldquo;Clear Quartz Crystal Point Earrings&rdquo;\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"wd-action-icon\"><span class=\"wd-check-icon\"></span></span><span class=\"wd-action-text\">Select options</span></a>\t<span id=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23468\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">\n\t\tThis product has multiple variants. The options may be chosen on the product page\t</span>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ About Crystals for Dreams</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can crystals help me remember or control my dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Not directly. Crystals can&#8217;t grant dream recall or lucid dreams. Many people keep one by the bed as a tangible cue to pay attention to dreams; recall itself comes from practice, not the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are crystals scientifically proven to affect dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">No. There is no clinical evidence that crystals influence dreams. Any felt benefit usually comes from the ritual of setting an intention or reflecting on waking, not a proven effect of the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal is best for dream recall and lucid dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Herkimer diamond is the most commonly chosen — long tied to dreamwork and attunement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal for calm, less troubled dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Amethyst and lepidolite — amethyst to settle the mind, lepidolite for steadier nights.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal helps me understand my dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Labradorite is often used for sitting with dream symbolism after waking.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How should I cleanse dream crystals?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Smoke (sage, palo santo), sound (singing bowl), or moonlight work for most stones. Note that selenite is water-sensitive — keep it dry and avoid water cleansing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal bracelet for dreams?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">An amethyst bracelet is the most common first choice — easy to wear into the evening and glance at as a cue to set a dream intention.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Explore More Crystal Guides</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-sleep/\">Crystals for Sleep</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-spiritual/\">Crystals for Spiritual</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-intuition/\">Crystals for Intuition</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-meditation/\">Crystals for Meditation</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-peace/\">Crystals for Peace</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Dreams ask for a little attention to stick — and a real stone by the bed can be a steady cue to hold them. Start with one and let a small habit add up. For more, explore <a href=\"/spiritual-connection/\">Spiritual Connection</a>.</p>\n",
